---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { AUTHOR } from '../../consts';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="ko"
  title="연락처"
  description="문의 환영합니다."
  pathname="/ko/contact"
>
  <article class="container-prose pt-20 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mb-8" style="line-height: 1.2;">연락처</h1>
    <p class="mb-8" style="color: var(--fg-soft);">
      Technical Support Engineering, AI-native 개발자 도구, MCP 서버, 가상화, 네트워크 인프라에
      관한 대화 환영합니다. {AUTHOR.location}.
    </p>

    <dl class="space-y-3">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-24 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--fg-soft);">이메일</dt>
        <dd><a href={`mailto:${AUTHOR.email}`}>{AUTHOR.email}</a></dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-24 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--fg-soft);">
          LinkedIn
        </dt>
        <dd>
          <a href={AUTHOR.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            linkedin.com/in/macer-p-993b27366
          </a>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-24 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--fg-soft);">GitHub</dt>
        <dd>
          <a href={AUTHOR.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/Macer-Park</a>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <dt class="w-24 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--fg-soft);">언어</dt>
        <dd>한국어 (Native) · 영어 (Professional) · 일본어 (JLPT N1)</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
